<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="Payment Terms & Methods for Vidyari. Learn about accepted payment methods, security, and billing information.">
  <title>Payment Terms - Vidyari</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="./images/logo.svg">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    :root {
      /* Strictly Monochrome Professional Palette */
      --bg-body: #ffffff;      /* Pure white background */
      --text-primary: #000000; /* Jet black for headings */
      --text-body: #1a1a1a;    /* Near black for high contrast reading */
      --text-muted: #555555;   /* Gray for metadata */
      --border-light: #e5e5e5; /* Light divider lines */
      --border-strong: #000000; /* Strong structural lines */
      --bg-box: #f9f9f9;       /* Very light gray for section boxes */
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: var(--bg-body);
      color: var(--text-body);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* --- Layout Container: Full Width --- */
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 60px;
    }

    /* --- Typography --- */
    h1 {
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    h2 {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-top: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-strong);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    h2 i { font-size: 1.2rem; }

    h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 1.5em;
      max-width: 100%;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    /* --- Header --- */
    header {
      margin-bottom: 60px;
      padding-bottom: 40px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    }

    .back-link {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .meta-info {
      display: flex;
      gap: 30px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-family: 'Inter', monospace;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--border-strong);
      padding-left: 15px;
    }

    .meta-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }

    /* --- Notice Box --- */
    .notice-box {
      width: 100%;
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 30px;
      background-color: var(--bg-box);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .notice-icon { font-size: 24px; color: var(--text-primary); }
    .notice-content { font-weight: 500; font-size: 1rem; }

    /* --- Payment Methods Grid --- */
    .payment-methods {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .payment-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
      padding: 30px;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .payment-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--text-primary);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .payment-icon {
      color: var(--text-primary);
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .payment-card strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    /* --- Tables --- */
    .table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 30px 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .table th, .table td {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .table th {
      background-color: var(--bg-box);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-strong);
    }

    /* --- Lists --- */
    ul { margin: 20px 0; padding-left: 25px; }
    li { margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 5px; }

    /* --- Billing Contact Box --- */
    .billing-box {
      background: var(--bg-box);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    /* --- Footer --- */
    footer {
      margin-top: 100px;
      padding: 50px 0;
      border-top: 4px solid var(--border-strong);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    footer p { margin: 0; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
    
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 30px; }
    
    footer a { color: var(--text-primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    
    a { color: var(--text-primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* --- Responsive --- */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container { padding: 30px 20px; }
      h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
      .meta-info { flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
      .payment-methods { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .footer-links { flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Home</a>
      <h1>Payment Terms & Methods</h1>
      <div class="meta-info">
        <div class="meta-item">
          <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
          <span>UPDATED: FEBRUARY 2026</span>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-item">
          <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
          <span>SECURE PAYMENTS</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="notice-box">
      <div class="notice-icon"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i></div>
      <div class="notice-content">
        Vidyari supports multiple secure payment methods. All transactions are processed through Cashfree Payment Gateway with PCI DSS Level 1 compliance and 256-bit SSL/TLS encryption to protect your financial information.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i> Accepted Payment Methods</h2>
      <div class="payment-methods">
        
        <div class="payment-card">
          <div class="payment-icon"><i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i></div>
          <strong>Credit & Debit Cards</strong>
          <p>Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Rupay. Processed securely via Cashfree.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="payment-card">
          <div class="payment-icon"><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i></div>
          <strong>Digital Wallets</strong>
          <p>GPay, PhonePe, PayTM, BHIM. Instant processing and confirmation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="payment-card">
          <div class="payment-icon"><i class="fas fa-bank"></i></div>
          <strong>Bank Transfers</strong>
          <p>NetBanking, UPI. Direct transfer from your bank account.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="payment-card">
          <div class="payment-icon"><i class="fas fa-exchange-alt"></i></div>
          <strong>UPI Payments</strong>
          <p>All UPI apps supported. Standard transaction fees apply.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"></i> Pricing & Currency</h2>
      
      <h3>Official Currency</h3>
      <p>All prices on Vidyari are displayed in Indian Rupees (INR). Prices include applicable 18% GST unless otherwise stated.</p>
      
      <h3>Tax Information</h3>
      <p>GST is automatically calculated and included in displayed prices. Tax invoices are available for download.</p>
      
      <h3>Price Changes</h3>
      <p>Vidyari reserves the right to change prices at any time. Prices listed at checkout are final.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Payment Security</h2>
      
      <h3>Security Standards</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>PCI DSS Level 1 Compliance</li>
        <li>256-bit SSL/TLS Encryption</li>
        <li>Tokenization Technology</li>
        <li>No full card information storage</li>
        <li>Cashfree Payment Gateway Processing</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3>Fraud Prevention</h3>
      <p>We employ industry-standard fraud detection systems. Unauthorized transactions are investigated promptly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-history"></i> Transaction Status & Records</h2>
      
      <h3>Order Confirmation</h3>
      <p>Immediate confirmation email with Order ID and Transaction ID after successful payment.</p>
      
      <h3>Invoice Access</h3>
      <p>Full invoices with GST breakdown available in your Account Dashboard under Transactions.</p>
      
      <h3>Processing Times</h3>
      <table class="table">
        <tr>
          <th>Payment Method</th>
          <th>Processing Time</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Credit/Debit Card</td>
          <td>Real-time</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Digital Wallets</td>
          <td>Real-time</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>NetBanking</td>
          <td>5-30 minutes</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>UPI</td>
          <td>Real-time</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i> Failed & Retry Transactions</h2>
      
      <h3>Transaction Failures</h3>
      <p>If a transaction fails, you will not be charged. Failed transactions are cleared within 24 hours.</p>
      
      <h3>Retry Attempts</h3>
      <p>You can immediately retry payment using the same or different payment method without additional fees.</p>
      
      <h3>Duplicate Charges</h3>
      <p>If accidentally charged twice, our billing team investigates and issues refunds within 5-7 business days.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Billing Support</h2>
      <div class="billing-box">
        <p><strong>Billing Email:</strong> billing@vidyari.com</p>
        <p><strong>Response Time:</strong> 24 hours</p>
        <p><strong>Contact for:</strong> Payment issues, invoices, billing inquiries, duplicate charges</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <div>
        <p>&copy; 2025-2026 Vidyari. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
     
    </footer>

  </div>
</body>
</html>